commit.message: tests: TestClient: Add function to mock stream management state
tests: message: Fix deprecation warning when testing isFallback()
Introduce Algorithms header with transform() function

RosterManager: Fix emitting rosterReceived() before items are stored

This caused the roster to be empty in the moment when the signal was
emitted.
MessagePrivate: Modernize by using default values instead of ctor

Update XEP-0428: Fallback Indication to v0.2

Introduces new QXmppFallback class for providing the new body/subject
text references.

https://xmpp.org/extensions/xep-0428.html
Utils: Add integer parsing helpers for all common int types
doc: doap: Add SASL 2 support
IncomingClient: Implement basic SASL 2 authentication support

Configuration: Disable PLAIN authentication mechanism by default

It is recommended to disable PLAIN, even with TLS, for references see:
 * SASL 2: https://xmpp.org/extensions/xep-0388.html#security
 * RFC6120: https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc6120#section-13.8.3
tests: sasl: Add SaslManager case with disabled mechanisms
Configuration: Add option to disable SASL mechanisms
Sasl2Manager: Send user agent if configured
Configuration: Add SASL 2 user agent option
Sasl2: Add public Sasl2UserAgent wrapper class
OutgoingClient: Integrate Sasl2Manager
Configuration: Add option to disable SASL 2
tests: sasl: Add some Sasl2Manager tests
Sasl2: Implement basic Sasl2Manager

AuthenticationError: Add RequiredTasks enumerator

This can occur with SASL 2: the server may request us to complete tasks
that we may not support.
Sasl2: Implement parsing of all basic SASL 2 packets
Sasl2: Implement stream feature
Constants: Add SASL 2 and Bind 2 XML namespaces
SaslManager: Take availableMechanisms instead of whole StreamFeatures
SaslManager: Split up generation of initial response into func
SaslServer: Modernize API by using std::unique_ptr in create()
SaslClient: Modernize API by using std::unique_ptr in create()
SaslClient: Modernize API by using std::optional
